message: I've continued and implemented a practical solver in solution.py: an exact O(n^2) interval DP for n <= 2000 (verified against brute-force on many small random tests and the samples) and a fast heap-based greedy fallback for large n. I updated evaluation.txt to reflect the new assessment. All changes are saved.
